               <p>Prisoner's Defence. A boy put it into my pocket, and then said,</p>
               <p>"What have you got in your pocket;" the gentleman said I was not the boy who took it.</p>
               <p>MR. SANDERSON. I said, I thought there was another in company with him.</p>
